  "title" : "Generating a Random Number between 1 and 10 Java",
  "body" : "<p>I want to generate a number between 1 and 10 in Java.</p>\n\n<p>Here is what I tried:</p>\n\n<pre><code>Random rn = new Random();\nint answer = rn.nextInt(10) + 1;\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Is there a way to tell what to put in the parenthesis <code>()</code> when calling the nextInt method and what to add? </p>\n"
